<content>1: # Stage 1: Frontend build
2: FROM node:18-alpine AS frontend-builder
3: 
4: WORKDIR /app
5: 
6: # Copy only frontend package files
7: COPY frontend/package*.json ./
8: RUN npm ci
9: 
10: # Copy frontend source code
11: COPY frontend/ ./
12: 
13: # Build frontend with Vite
14: RUN npm run build
15: 
16: # Stage 2: Frontend runtime
17: FROM nginx:alpine
18: 
19: # Copy frontend build to nginx
20: COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
21: 
22: # Configure nginx
23: RUN echo 'server { listen 80; root /usr/share/nginx/html; location / { try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html; } }' > /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
24: 
25: EXPOSE 80
26: 
27: # Stage 3: Go API build
28: FROM golang:1.21-alpine AS api-builder
29: 
30: WORKDIR /app
31: 
32: # Copy only Go package files
33: COPY api/go.mod api/go.sum ./
34: 
35: # Download dependencies
36: RUN go mod download
37: 
38: # Copy Go source code
39: COPY api/ ./
40: 
41: # Build Go API
42: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -o server .
43: 
44: # Stage 4: API runtime
45: FROM alpine
46: 
47: RUN apk --no-cache add ca-certificates
48: 
49: WORKDIR /root/
50: 
51: COPY --from=api-builder /app/server .
52: 
53: EXPOSE 8080
54: 
55: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
56:   CMD wget --no-verbose --tries=1 --spider http://localhost:8080/healthz || exit 1
57: 
58: CMD ["./server"]
59: 
60: # Stage 5: Python Celery build
61: FROM python:3.11-slim AS worker-builder
62: 
63: WORKDIR /app
64: 
65: # Copy only Python requirements
66: COPY worker/requirements.txt ./
67: 
68: # Install dependencies
69: RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
70: 
71: # Copy Python source code
72: COPY worker/ ./
73: 
74: # Stage 6: Celery worker runtime
75: FROM python:3.11-slim
76: 
77: WORKDIR /app
78: 
79: RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
80:     gcc \
81:     && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
82: 
83: COPY --from=worker-builder /app/requirements.txt .
84: COPY --from=worker-builder /app/worker/ .
85: RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
86: 
87: CMD ["celery", "-A", "worker", "worker", "--loglevel=info"]
88: 
89: # Build targets
90: # --target frontend-builder: builds and runs frontend with nginx
91: # --target api-builder: builds and runs Go API server
92: # --target worker-builder: builds and runs Celery worker
